{"id":"mem_1774563662982_hafcud","title":"MISTAKE: Said 'done' and 'deployed' without curl-checking the live UR","content":"What went wrong: Said 'done' and 'deployed' without curl-checking the live URL for the actual new code. Did this 3+ times in one session.\nHow to avoid: Never claim deployment is complete without first curling the live URL and grep-confirming the specific new code is present. Wait for Railway build cycle (3-5 min) before verifying.","category":"error","importance":"high","tags":["feedback","negative","verification","deployment","trust","claiming-done-without-proof"],"rubricSummary":null,"bayesian":{"priorProbability":0.118,"uncertainty":0.046,"observations":147,"lastUpdated":"2026-03-26T22:21:02.985Z"},"diagnosis":{"rootCauseCategory":"tool_output_misread","criticalFailureStep":"feedback_capture","violations":[],"evidence":[{"type":"context","value":"Claimed dashboard features were deployed multiple times before verifying Railway had actually rebuilt and served the new code"}]},"sourceFeedbackId":"fb_1774563662976_qs1ha3","timestamp":"2026-03-26T22:21:02.976Z","revisedFromId":"mem_1774037681897_kjped5","pruned":true,"pruneReason":"high_entropy_contradiction"}
